plenty of corn bread
and chitlins here tonight.

242
00:20:38,253 --> 00:20:40,221
Do it, Cy. Do it for your papa.

243
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:42,916
What did he get?

244
00:20:51,199 --> 00:20:54,532
- Lord save us, look at that gal.
