294
00:24:55,844 --> 00:24:59,211
<i>Now just imitate the way a waiter</i>

295
00:24:59,281 --> 00:25:01,306
<i>Walks with a plate of chow</i>

296
00:25:01,516 --> 00:25:04,144
<i>Why, you needn't wait to do it later</i>

297
00:25:04,519 --> 00:25:06,885
