298
00:25:06,955 --> 00:25:09,355
<i>Come with me where Dixie marches</i>

299
00:25:09,791 --> 00:25:11,986
<i>Marches on its fallen arches</i>

300
00:25:12,460 --> 00:25:15,725
<i>And see them Swanee Shuffle along</i>

301
00:25:16,431 --> 00:25:19,798
<i>Learn to do the Swanee Shuffle</i>

