Leave her here with me.

835
01:05:26,636 --> 01:05:28,831
You go on there back to your people.

836
01:05:36,746 --> 01:05:38,509
Oh, God!

837
01:05:42,519 --> 01:05:44,646
Have mercy on me!

838
01:05:46,656 --> 01:05:49,090
Here, what's the matter with you, gal?

839
01:05:50,026 --> 01:05:53,393
Ain't nothing. I know what it is.

840
01:05:53,496 --> 01:05:57,762
Yes, you got more religion
than what's good for you...

841
01:05:58,101 --> 01:05:59,159
you hypocrite!

842
01:06:00,336 --> 01:06:02,201
Come on up here, Christmas!

843
01:06:03,373 --> 01:06:06,536
You're slower than cold molasses
in the winter time.

844
01:06:06,776 --> 01:06:08,175
Come on up here.

845
