What are you doing here, Hot Shot?
What are you doing here?

938
01:11:59,762 --> 01:12:03,459
So you're all hopped up about
that fake preacher, huh?

939
01:12:03,699 --> 01:12:07,499
Go on, Hot Shot, leave me be.
